tierd (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package for tierd + tierd-cli. Ships the Go
    daemon at /usr/sbin/tierd, the operator CLI at
    /usr/bin/tierd-cli, and a systemd unit at
    /lib/systemd/system/tierd.service. State dir /var/lib/tierd/
    is created + owned by root in postinst.

